show.title: Baap, Beti aur Black Money
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/d99H4C
show.description: Baap, Beti aur Black Money tells the story of Suresh, a humble watchman whose life changes overnight when his daughter inherits her late husband’s drug empire and shares her fortune with him. Once humiliated and broken, Suresh rises to power, using his newfound wealth to take revenge on those who betrayed him — and to finally reclaim the dignity and love he was once denied.
